data.description: An absolutely gorgeous extensively remodeled & spacious home awaits you in the lovely Smiling Hill neighborhood! No expense was spared on both interior & exterior. This home has been transformed into an airy, open floor plan full of space & beauty. You will immediately notice the impeccable detail in the attractive landscaping & convenience of the additional concrete added to the drive, running all the way back to the double gates into the backyard. When you enter the home, the natural light, large living area & immediate view into the screened in back patio/game room impress. A large study/den/bonus living space with gorgeous, oversized barn doors sits across from the open dining space. The living room displays its statement piece - a gorgeous stone fireplace, sturdy hearth, framed by built in bookcases. The fully equipped kitchen with beautiful island bar, all stainless steel appliances & new granite countertops makes this the heart of the home an entertainer's dream! Open the french doors to the screened patio & accommodate a large dinner party & enjoy a game of pool - all items present will remain! The large Master Suite is a total oasis. Gorgeous glass barn doors lead you into the huge master bath with his & her sinks, granite counter tops, custom tiled 4x6 full walk-in shower with double rain shower heads will have you in awe. You can't miss the huge walk-in closet & custom conveniences. You will feel like you're on vacation at home with a gorgeous view of the greenery in the back yard & fantastic space. Two secondary bedrooms are split by a spacious hall bath with custom tiled double vanities & shower. A shaded dog run sits on the east side of the home with a concrete pathway that's gated to front & back yard. This home offers a quiet neighborhood lifestyle, down the street from a school & a park, yet only minutes to restaurants, shopping, & interstate access - 1/2 mi to Turnpike, 2.4 mi to I-35 & 1 mi to Brdwy Ext. A full list of all updates can be provided.
